01:23:31,697 --> 01:23:35,252
那么现在的问题就是，这位新蚁人是谁呢？
which begs the question, who is the new Ant-Man?

1238
01:23:35,348 --> 01:23:39,681
我敬爱的导师比起我来更信任的这个人，是谁呢？
Who is the man that my beloved mentor trusted even more than me?

1239
01:23:41,385 --> 01:23:44,185
斯科特·朗
Scott Lang.

1240
01:23:45,033 --> 01:23:46,753
可怜的家伙
The martyr

1241
01:23:46,771 --> 01:23:49,611
他为他的行为付出了代价
who took on the system and paid the price,

1242
01:23:49,614 --> 01:23:53,397
家已经毁了，唯一的女儿也离他而去
losing his family and his only daughter in the process,

1243
01:23:53,403 --> 01:23:56,283
跟你还真是像啊，汉克
exactly your kind of guy, Hank.

1244
01:23:57,591 --> 01:24:02,858
他没有留下任何痕迹就从监狱中逃跑了
He escapes his jail cell without leaving any clue as to how,

1245
01:24:02,861 --> 01:24:04,001
然后呢
and then,

1246
01:24:04,223 --> 01:24:06,423
就这样直接消失了
he disappears magically,

1247
01:24:07,222 --> 01:24:13,564
连值多少钱都还不知道呢，他就把这件蚁人制服送来了
despite having no money to his name, and now he brings me the Ant-Man suit,

1248
01:24:14,470 --> 01:24:18,522
这个唯一可以和我的作品媲美的东西
the only thing that can rival my creation.

1249
01:24:18,632 --> 01:24:21,574
达伦，不要这么做
Darren, don't do this.

1250
01:24:21,961 --> 01:24:25,705
如果你卖给这些人，这个世界会变得一团糟的
If you sell to these men, it's going to be chaos.

1251
01:24:25,709 --> 01:24:29,503
我已经卖了，而且多亏了你，卖了双倍的价钱呢
I already have, and for twice the price, thanks to you.

1252
01:24:30,636 --> 01:24:34,112
