It's not easy to successfully infiltrate an Avengers facility.

1253
01:24:34,115 --> 01:24:36,515
幸亏这件事儿传得快
Thankfully, word travels fast.

1254
01:24:36,678 --> 01:24:41,078
哦，我只卖给了他们黄蜂装甲，粒子我可没给他们
Oh I'll sell them the Yellowjacket but I'm keeping the particle to myself.

1255
01:24:41,135 --> 01:24:42,602
那可是装甲的燃料
They don't run on diesel.

1256
01:24:42,644 --> 01:24:45,844
如果想使用装甲，就得来找我买燃料哦
If you want the fuel you'll have to come to me.

1257
01:24:46,721 --> 01:24:51,821
如果一个人可以控制世界上最具有力量的武器的话，那他就是？
What do you call the only man who can arm the most powerful weapon in the world?

1258
01:24:52,056 --> 01:24:54,763
世界上最有力量的人
The most powerful man in the world.

1259
01:24:54,976 --> 01:24:56,438
你为我骄傲了吗？
You proud of me yet?

1260
01:24:56,442 --> 01:24:59,828
你可以阻止这一切的，达伦，现在还不晚
You can stop this, Darren. It's not too late.

1261
01:24:59,834 --> 01:25:02,361
这一刻已经来的太迟了
It's been too late for a long time now.

1262
01:25:04,276 --> 01:25:05,146
达伦
Darren.

1263
01:25:07,367 --> 01:25:08,634
你在干什么？
What are you doing?

1264
01:25:08,682 --> 01:25:11,915
他根本就没有能力照顾好你，就像对我一样
He wasn't any more capable of caring for you than he was for me.

1265
01:25:11,940 --> 01:25:16,940
这不是真正的你，你的思想已经被粒子影响了
This is not who you are. It's the particles altering your brain chemistry.

1266
01:25:24,850 --> 01:25:27,250
等下，等下，等一下
Wait, wait wait wait wait wait wait.

1267
01:25:28,020 --> 01:25:29,020
你说的太对了
You're right.

1268
01:25:29,538 --> 01:25:31,538
这才是我应该做的
I have to be the one to do it.

1269
01:25:33,540 --> 01:25:34,540
来吧咱们
Here we go.

1270
01:25:36,235 --> 01:25:39,135
把，枪，放，下
Drop. Your. Gun.

1271
01:25:42,310 --> 01:25:45,509
你知道么，那天晚上我本来是要去他家杀他的
