1280
01:26:26,397 --> 01:26:28,430
汉克，听我说，你会没事的
Hank. Listen, you're gonna be okay.

1281
01:26:28,514 --> 01:26:30,081
好吗？你一定会没事的
All right, you're gonna be just fine.

1282
01:26:30,738 --> 01:26:35,005
