Take the suit off or I'll blow your brains out and peel it off.

1283
01:27:00,173 --> 01:27:03,773
皮娒科技有情况，呼号10-33，请求支援
We got a 10-33 at Pym Tech, request immediate backup.

1284
01:27:03,879 --> 01:27:04,879
快走！快走！
Go, go, go.

1285
01:27:17,698 --> 01:27:20,097
送我到屋顶，准备好通讯
Get me to the roof and radio ahead.

1286
01:27:21,375 --> 01:27:24,208
我要直升机马上就能起飞
I want to make sure the helicopter's ready to take off.

1287
01:27:24,239 --> 01:27:27,772
你们俩，只要是从那里面出来的全部给我干掉
You two, kill anything that comes out of that vault.

1288
01:27:28,512 --> 01:27:29,512
爸爸
Dad,

1289
01:27:29,920 --> 01:27:30,920
你能动吗？
can you move?

1290
01:27:33,507 --> 01:27:35,574
我们得带他离开
We need to get him out of here.

1291
01:27:36,201 --> 01:27:39,168
去，拿，那件装甲
Go. Get. That suit.

1292
