Feels kinda, kinda weird, y'know.

1301
01:28:39,036 --> 01:28:40,969
是么，可是还没完事儿呢
Yeah. But we're not done yet.

1302
01:28:41,347 --> 01:28:44,014
赶紧在这里爆炸之前逃出去
Get outta here before this place blows.

1303
01:28:49,785 --> 01:28:50,785
我了个去！
Oh, dammit!

1304
01:28:51,467 --> 01:28:52,467
那个人
That guy.

1305
