And there's a tank.

1314
01:29:41,871 --> 01:29:42,871
帮我下
A little help.

1315
01:29:45,094 --> 01:29:46,094
我来吧
I got him.

1316
01:29:46,739 --> 01:29:47,873
我们需要医生
We need a doctor.

1317
