等一下！都给我从那个货车上下来！
Wait a minute. Get out of that van.

1322
01:30:44,174 --> 01:30:45,841
- 啥？ - 马上给我下来！
- What? - Get out of that van.

1323
01:30:45,933 --> 01:30:48,733
坦克声太大，我没听清楚
It's too loud there's a tank I can't hear you.

