你疯了吗？快把枪放下！
Are you crazy? Put the gun down!

1326
01:30:58,341 --> 01:30:59,341
窗户！
The windows!

1327
01:31:03,713 --> 01:31:07,013
你以为抢走这个就能阻止这一切了吗？
Did you think you could stop the future with a heist?

1328
01:31:07,082 --> 01:31:09,315
谁告诉你我光要抢这个啦
It was never just a heist.

1329
01:31:30,998 --> 01:31:32,131
把枪放下
Put the gun down.

1330
01:31:40,695 --> 01:31:43,828
我看见他了，就在那里，快点，快快快
I got him, I got him, there he is, go go go go

1331
01:32:00,075 --> 01:32:02,075
我们得找地方降落
Got to set her down somewhere.

1332
