快报警！
Call 911!

1335
01:33:33,868 --> 01:33:34,868
没事儿啦
It's okay.

1336
01:33:40,065 --> 01:33:41,598
警察！举起手来！
Police! Put your hands up.

1337
01:33:41,624 --> 01:33:42,624
举起来！
Get 'em up.

1338
01:33:44,375 --> 01:33:45,375
斯科特？
Scott?

1339
01:33:45,654 --> 01:33:46,654
帕克斯顿
Paxton.

1340
01:33:46,687 --> 01:33:48,354
你得听我解…
You have to listen to me-

1341
01:34:15,094 --> 01:34:17,360
帕克斯顿，快掉头送我回去
Paxton. Turn around, take me back.

1342
01:34:17,709 --> 01:34:19,542
我是在送你回去，回监狱去
I am taking you back. To prison.

1343
01:34:19,596 --> 01:34:22,096
那个后院里有样东西必须要被摧毁
There's something in that backyard that needs to be destroyed.

1344
01:34:22,193 --> 01:34:23,660
在捕蚊灯里面，它…
In the bug zapper, it-

1345
01:34:25,285 --> 01:34:27,019
你还是断了这个念头吧！
You need to desist right now!

1346
