嘿，小花生
Hi Peanut.

1363
01:35:32,031 --> 01:35:35,031
你倒是找个跟你一样大的打啊
Why don't you pick on someone your own size?

1364
01:35:47,619 --> 01:35:49,886
你想往哪藏呢，小家伙？
Now where'd you go, little guy?

1365
01:35:55,429 --> 01:35:56,429
抓到你了
There you are.

1366
01:35:56,887 --> 01:35:57,887
蛤蛤，蛤蛤
Ha ha ha ha.

1367
